### Crear transacción INCOME (ingreso)
POST http://localhost:3000/transaction
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "walletId": "6fc835fb-dc23-41a1-877e-bb781ac3d08c",
  "categoryId": "40beecab-9892-4253-87f1-ccc133d68132",
  "type": "INCOME",
  "name": "Salario septiembre",
  "amount": 200000,
  "date": "2025-09-12T15:00:00.000Z"
}

